title: FastCap HOD-DOUBLE Handle On Demand
features: The HOD DOUBLE is not meant for use on Laminate flooring because Laminate flooring has a texture. The suction cups of the HOD Double are meant for non textured surfaces such as windows, melamine.
Stop straining your back trying to lift heavy stuff. Suck it up with our Handle on Demand (HOD).
Comes in single or double. Just fasten the suction pads to any nonporous surface and move it, lift it, place it, & transport it with ease.
